[Name] PyEnchant
[Summary] A spellchecking library for Python.
[Description] PyEnchant is a set of language bindings and some wrapper
classes to make the excellent Enchant spellchecker available as a Python
module. The bindings are created using ctypes. It includes all the
functionality of Enchant with the flexibility of Python and a nice
"Pythonic" object-oriented interface. It also aims to provide some
higher-level functionality than is available in the C API.
